PN,34401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FA recovery truck driver who killed his
OL,7,Fteenage girlfriend by ramming her
OL,8,Fagainst a lamppost with his truck has
OL,9,Fbeen found guilty of her murder.
OL,11,FMohammed Azim, who is 41, murdered 19-
OL,12,Fyear-old Lily Whitehouse in Oldbury in
OL,13,FNovember last year on his 41st
OL,14,Fbirthday on November 5.
OL,16,FLily, who has been described as "full
OL,17,Fof light, laughter, and kindness," had
OL,18,Fjust returned from visiting her new
OL,19,Fbaby in hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FThe baby had been born prematurely and
OL,7,Fwas in the neo-natal intensive care
OL,8,Funit at Russells Hall Hospital.
OL,10,FThe pair had started dating when she
OL,11,Fwas 16 and he was 37 and had an on-off
OL,12,Frelationship. Lily had her baby with
OL,13,Fanother man.
OL,15,FOn 5 November 2025, Lily rang Azim
OL,16,Fafter her hospital visit and he picked
OL,17,Fher up. It's thought they argued, and
OL,18,FLily got out of the truck before Azim
OL,19,Fchased her down and drove the vehicle
OL,20,Finto her.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FCCTV footage captured him pushing her
OL,7,Fwith his truck and then, off camera,
OL,8,Fit's thought he pinned her against a
OL,9,Flamppost - which killed her.
OL,11,FDI Nigel Box from West Midlands Police
OL,12,Fsaid that Azim claimed another driver
OL,13,Fwas involved.
OL,15,F"Within two minutes of the collision,
OL,16,FMohammed Azim has placed Lily back
OL,17,Finto the recovery truck and he makes a
OL,18,F999 call, during which he fabricates a
OL,19,Fversion of events about what happened
OL,20,Fto Lily.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,F"He says that another car came along
OL,7,Fand hit Lily and ran her over, causing
OL,8,Fher injuries, and had driven off."
OL,10,FWhen he called 999 he repeated the
OL,11,Fclaim that she had been "hit by a car"
OL,12,Fand didn't offer her any help.
OL,14,FHe was captured on body camera once
OL,15,Fagain telling emergency crews he had
OL,16,Fchased after the car he claimed hit
OL,17,FLily as she was crossing the road.
OL,19,FAzim was arrested at the scene.JDI
OL,20,FNigel Box said Azim had never shown
OL,21,Fany remorse in court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,F"What was noticeable was that he was
OL,7,Freally focused on how this had
OL,8,Fimpacted on him and the fact that he
OL,9,Fwas in prison and the fact that he was
OL,10,Fbeing made to come and relive the
OL,11,Fevents of that night...
OL,13,F"... At no point did he acknowledge
OL,14,FLily's family and the devastation that
OL,15,Fhe'd caused them, and he never
OL,16,Facknowledged Lily at all."
OL,18,FLily had been looking forward to life
OL,19,Fas a mum, in a new flat which she was
OL,20,Fgetting ready for when the baby was
OL,21,Fready to come home.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FJudge Mr Justice Murray told Azim, of
OL,7,FTividale Road in Tipton, he would be
OL,8,Fsentenced on Monday 22 June after the
OL,9,Fjury returned their verdict by a
OL,10,Fmajority of 10 to two after less than
OL,11,Fsix hours of deliberation.
OL,13,FMembers of Ms Whitehouse's family in
OL,14,Fthe public gallery sobbed as the
OL,15,Fverdict was returned.
OL,17,FAddressing the defendant in the dock
OL,18,Fput his hands to his face, Mr Justice
OL,19,FMurray said: "Mr Azim you have been
OL,20,Ffound guilty of the murder of Lily
OL,21,FWhitehouse.
OL,26,@{D@NOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,F"You are remanded into custody. You
OL,7,Fwill be sentenced on Monday at 2pm.
OL,8,FYou may now go down."
OL,10,FThe trial heard Ms Whitehouse, who had
OL,11,Fjust been to visit her baby in a
OL,12,Fneonatal intensive care unit, was
OL,13,Fcrushed against a lamppost in Old Park
OL,14,FLane, Oldbury, by Azim's flatbed
OL,15,FMercedes Sprinter vehicle, causing
OL,16,Ffatal chest injuries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FA Home Office pathologist found Ms
OL,7,FWhitehouse had suffered injuries
OL,8,Fpredominantly to her right side while
OL,9,Fin an upright position, including a
OL,10,Fbroken upper arm, fractured ribs, a
OL,11,Flaceration to her liver and traumatic
OL,12,Finjuries to her chest, which caused
OL,13,F"severe bleeding" and led to her death.
OL,15,FGiving evidence during the trial, Ms
OL,16,FWhitehouse's aunt, Melissa Wheeler,
OL,17,Ftold the jury her niece had met Azim
OL,18,Fafter they exchanged numbers in West
OL,19,FBromwich High Street and began a
OL,20,Frelationship.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FDuring questioning by the prosecution,
OL,7,FMs Wheeler agreed that the victim had
OL,8,Fbeen "besotted" with Azim but that the
OL,9,Fpair would fight a lot and the
OL,10,Fdefendant would sometimes block Ms
OL,11,FWhitehouse when she tried to speak to
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FShe said she was aware that Azim was
OL,15,Fnot the father of Ms Whitehouse's baby
OL,16,Fand he was "not happy" that she was
OL,17,Fpregnant so she would hide her bump
OL,18,Fwith long clothing when she visited or
OL,19,Fstayed with him.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@OO]xD@LOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FMs Wheeler said her niece went into
OL,7,Flabour 10 weeks early after she fell
OL,8,Fto ground when Azim "sped off" in his
OL,9,Fvehicle.
OL,11,FLibby Higgs, a friend of the victim,
OL,12,Ftold the jury that Ms Whitehouse
OL,13,Fconfided in her that Azim would say
OL,14,F"vile" things to her and would punch
OL,15,Fher, which he claimed was playfighting.
OL,17,FIn his evidence, Azim denied ever
OL,18,Fbeing violent to Ms Whitehouse and
OL,19,Fsaid he was the only person who
OL,20,Fsupported her after she fell out with
OL,21,Fher family.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@^O]vD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FExplaining his version of events on
OL,7,Fthe night Ms Whitehouse was fatally
OL,8,Finjured, he said he picked her up
OL,9,Fafter she got off a bus from Russells
OL,10,FHall Hospital where she had been
OL,11,Fvisiting her baby and was going to
OL,12,Fdrop her home in Amber Drive, Oldbury.
OL,14,FMs Whitehouse allegedly asked him to
OL,15,Fsit with her for 10 minutes before she
OL,16,Fwent home, so he pulled up in Old Park
OL,17,FLane nearby because it was a wider
OL,18,Froad for his van and the two chatted
OL,19,Fand scrolled on their phones.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FHe said they had not argued and Ms
OL,7,FWhitehouse simply did not want to go
OL,8,Fhome so asked if she could stay with
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FAzim said he told her no as was tired
OL,12,Fand had to get up early for work but
OL,13,Fshe tried to stop him by going in
OL,14,Ffront of the van.
OL,16,FHe started to drive slowly to the left
OL,17,Fto go around Ms Whitehouse, he said,
OL,18,Fbut had to swerve back to the right
OL,19,Fbecause of parked cars.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FIn his evidence, Azim told the jury:
OL,7,F"I hear a bang at the back. It could
OL,8,Fhave been Lily jumping on the truck. I
OL,9,Ffelt something bump the back.
OL,11,F"I feel the back tyres, like something
OL,12,Fcome under the tyre or something drop
OL,13,Funder the tyre. I slammed the brake
OL,14,Fand straight away stopped.
OL,16,F"I looked back and saw Lily on the
OL,17,Ffloor in the middle of the road."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781902064
OL,3,CRecovery truck driver murdered new mum
OL,4,Cby ramming her against lamppost
OL,6,FThe court heard Azim came to the UK in
OL,7,F2001 from Pakistan around the age of
OL,8,F14 and went to college and worked in
OL,9,Ftakeaway restaurants to learn English.
OL,11,FHe was married in 2007 but had been
OL,12,Fsingle and living alone since his
OL,13,Fmarriage ended in 2015.
OL,15,FThe defendant told the jury Ms
OL,16,FWhitehouse relied on him for support
OL,17,Fand that she did not have many
OL,18,Ffriends, so would text and call him
OL,19,Foften while he was working.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
